    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Fresh out of the Academy, you are ready to make your way into history as a Genin. You were assigned in a team of three with a Jounin supervisor.</p><p><b>Source:</b> Mechanics/Character_Options/Occupations/Academy Student.md</p><p><b>Category:</b> Core</p><p><b>Prerequisite:</b> Age 10+</p><p><b>Class Skills:</b> Select 3 from Balance, Bluff, Climb, Chakra Control, Craft (chemical), Disable Device, Disguise, Escape Artist, Fuinjutsu, Gather Information, Genjutsu, Hide, Investigate, Knowledge (ninja lore), Knowledge (tactics), Ninjutsu, Sleight of Hand, Survival, Taijutsu.</p><p><b>Feat:</b> Select one from Archaic Weapon Proficiency, Brawl, Combat Martial Arts, Defensive Martial Arts, Genin, Genjutsu Adept, Nin Weapons Proficiency, Ninjutsu Adept, Taijutsu Adept.</p><p><b>Wealth Bonus Increase:</b> +1</p>"
